cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use sIfA in published work, please cite it using the metadata below."
title: "sIfA Tool — Statement of Intellectual Fellowship and Accountability"
abstract: >-
  A browser-based tool for declaring how AI tools contributed to a piece of
  research, mapped onto the 14 CRediT contributor roles. Produces a structured
  table and a single-page visualisation (the "sIfA figure") that can be
  attached to a publication, report, or institutional disclosure.
type: software
authors:
